      "value": "<p>Costing twice as much as any other sling model (minimum 1 sp), pony slings are designed to be attached to the leg of the pony, to be loaded with their mouth and propelled with a swing of that leg. Using this causes the pony to become slower, lowering their Speed by 10 feet until the start of their next turn. Despite being called a pony sling, it works equally well for any creature with the fingerless trait.</p>",
